7136.name: Fruit Basket
7136.description: A basket full of fruit. Emily asked you to bring it to her.

7137.name: Avellan Spice
7137.description: Spice imported from Avella. Has a special fragrance. Emily asked you to bring it to her.

7138.name: Honey Pouch
7138.description: Well sealed pouch of honey collected from bees. Take this to Emily.

7139.name: Bracelet of Lizardman
7139.description: A bracelet that Leto Lizardman wears. Take this to Guard Rath in Town of Giran.

7140.name: Cross of Einhasad
7140.description: A holy item that was found in the Forest of the Dead. Take this to the priest of the Rune Township.

7141.name: Cross of Einhasad
7141.description: A holy cross that was found in the Forest of the Dead. The Priest of the Rune Township returned it to you. Take this to Dark Elf Magister Tifaren.

7142.name: Lost Skull of Elf
7142.description: A skull of an elf that Grand Magister Tifaren asked you to bring.

7143.name: Letter of Innocentin
7143.description: A contract between High Priest Innocentin and the dead explorer is in this letter.

7144.name: Jewel of Adventurer
7144.description: Jewel that the explorer possessed. The color of jewel changes by the explorer's call.

7145.name: Jewel of Adventurer
7145.description: Jewel that the explorer possessed. The color of jewel changes by the explorer's call.

7146.name: Sealed Report Box
7146.description: Explorer's report box. It is sealed multiple times. Take this to the ghost of the explorer.

7147.name: Report Box
7147.description: Explorer's report box. The box is locked. Take this to High Priest Innocentin.

7148.name: Lidia's Hairpin
7148.description: Lidia's hair pin that has moonlight flower shape.

7149.name: Silver Key
7149.description: A silver spear is engraved on this key. There must be a lock that can be opened with this key.

7150.name: Silver Spear
7150.description: A reward that is given to the family with highest merit by the royal member of Elmore land. It is a model spear thus it has no P. Atk.

7151.name: Suspicious Totem Doll
7151.description: A totem doll you have obtained while hunting black magi according to the instructions of Lidia's maid. Take this to the mysterious magus and question him.

7152.name: Flower Bouquet
7152.description: A flower bouquet that Dorian asked you to lay at the gravestone in the south.

7153.name: Silver Cross of Einhasad
7153.description: A talisman given by Dorian. He asked you to find information about the monsters that appear in the Forest of the Dead at night.

7154.name: Broken Silver Cross of Einhasad
7154.description: A talisman given by Dorian. It seems to have been cracked by a powerful force.

7155.name: Lidia's Dress
7155.description: A red dress that was unearthed from the grave of Rose. It exhibits an aristocratic taste.

7156.name: Suspicious Totem Doll
7156.description: The totem doll that was returned by the mysterious magus. Take it to the priests of the Rune Township and question them about it.

7157.name: Gemstone Key
7157.description: A gemstone studded key. It has a nickname of "bejeweled staff" that indicates the authority of the king.

7158.name: Suspicious Totem Doll
7158.description: A suspicious totem doll that one obtains after slaying the underlings of Triol.

7160.name: Luxury Wine
7160.description: Premium wine that is on delivery.

7161.name: Skein of Yarn
7161.description: Yarn made of twisted spider web. Tenacious and sturdy.

7162.name: Rough Jewel
7162.description: Rough stone of jewel. Becomes a beautiful jewel when processed.

7163.name: Enchanted Iron
7163.description: Sturdier than generic iron. Tools made of this iron are said to be priceless.

7164.name: Signet Ring
7164.description: A seal that represents noble family.

7165.name: Map
7165.description: A map that is drawn for Miki the Cat.

7166.name: Medicinal Herb
7166.description: A medicinal herb that Miki the Cat found in Devil's Isle. Gentler is in need of this herb.

7167.name: Crystal of Seal
7167.description: A crystal that is used to activate the sealing in the altar.

7168.name: Blood of Saint
7168.description: Saint's blood that has power of holiness.

7169.name: Blood of Saint
7169.description: The blood obtained at the time of Kel Mahum's death. It contains the power of Einhasad.

7170.name: Seal of Light
7170.description: A seal from a Mysterious Necromancer. It uses the power of light.

7171.name: Bead of Obedience
7171.description: A gem from Kel Mahum that has power of Einhasad.

7172.name: Gem of Saints
7172.description: A gem that is left after the cremation of a saint. It has power of holiness.

7173.name: Feather Ornament
7173.description: A warrior symbol for Langk Lizardman.

7174.name: Tooth of Totem
7174.description: A tooth that has mysterious power.

7175.name: Tooth of Dragon
7175.description: A tooth of Langk Lizardman Commanders that strengthens their warriors.

7176.name: Letter of Iris
7176.description: A letter from Iris to Magister Rohmer in the Town of Gludio.

7177.name: Letter of Rohmer
7177.description: A letter from Rohmer to Magister Iris in Gludin Village.

7178.name: Black Bone Necklace
7178.description: A charm of Maille Lizardman Warriors.

7179.name: Red Bone Necklace
7179.description: A charm of Maille Lizardman Commanders.

7180.name: Incense Pouch
7180.description: A pouch of incense with mysterious scent.

7181.name: Gem of Maille Lizardman
7181.description: A gem of Maille Lizardman that has mysterious power.

7182.name: Patrol's Report
7182.description: A report from Guard Praga to Magister Rohmer.

7184.description: A gem in Araneid's head that controls them.

7187.description: Nepenthes seed used by Varka Silenos as currency.

7188.description: Certificate acquired when one becomes an avenger.

7189.description: A mark that proves membership of Daimon's family.

7190.name: Evil Spirit of Darkness
7190.description: An object substantiating the intrinsic darkness of Daimon the White-Eyed.

7191.name: Broken Crystal
7191.description: A fraction of the crystal used to summon Daimon.

7192.name: Unfinished Summon Crystal
7192.description: A fraction of the crystal used to summon Daimon. Still in an unfinished state.

7193.name: Summon Crystal
7193.description: A crystal used to summon Daimon. Emits golden shine.

7194.name: Essence of Daimon
7194.description: A dark crystal that constitutes Daimon.

7195.name: Boiled Eggs
7195.description: Delicious eggs boiled in spring water.
